Mod.name: Acolyte Fight 7.0
Mod.author: Mr7
Mod.description: Welcome to The M-7's first mod

flamestrike.name: Fireslice
flamestrike.description: Send a line of flame damaging your enemy.

meteorite.description: Slow moving orb that does no damage but gives huge health gain when oppenet is hit.
meteorite.name: Health Orb

kamehameha.name: Lazer Beam
kamehameha.description: Unleash a beam so powerful it wipes out all projectiles.

effects.title: Interruptible
effects.text: If you take an enemy hit, Lazer Beam will be interrupted.

drain.description: Shot an explosive starbomb at your enemey with redirect at cursor point.
drain.name: Starbomb

saber.name: Transport Saber
saber.description: For 1 secounds swing you will summon a sword that teleports your oppenets and enemys projectiles into the location you striked them at. The faster you swing, the farther they go.

shield.description: Reflect away projectile attacks. Ineffective against area-of-effect spells or Ghostball.

voidRush.description: For 3 seconds, increase movement speed 85%, and also become immune to damage from the void.

Orbiter.name: Orbiter
Orbiter.description: Around and around you. Keep following your enemies at orbital distance until it hits.

Flamestrike.name: Flamestrike
Flamestrike.description: Each bolt of Difire will add another stack of 2.5 damage per second to your enemy. There is no limit to the number of stacks, but you must hit them with Difire at least once every 4 seconds to keep the fire burning.

whirlwind1.name: Dragons Breath
whirlwind1.description: A firey whirlwind to harm your enemies and deals 15 damage. The whirlwind also catches enemy projectiles.

effects.title: Slow
effects.text: Enemies caught in your Dragon Breath will be slowed 30% for 1 seconds and damaged 10hp every secound.

Whipe.description: Quickly yank your enemy towards you.
Whipe.name: Whip

grappled.description: Hold the button to grapple. Move your cursor to swing Grapple around. Throw your enemies into the void!

Ghostball.name: Ghostball
Ghostball.description: Send a ball that travles thru objects and projectiles.

BodyShock.name: BodyShock
BodyShock.description: Get in close to shock your enemys with electricly coming from your body

effects.title: Fast
effects.text: Gain a 15% movement speed bonus for 3 seconds (even if you miss).

LightStamp.name: LightStamp
LightStamp.description: Place a lightbulb in your exact positon. Only shatters when middle is touched by enemeys or within 4 seconds.'

telep0rt.description: Teleport to a nearby location. Get close, or get away.

effects.title: Weak
effects.text: For 0.25 seconds after teleporting, you will only deal 25% damage and cannot deal fatal damage.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

Shine Slice.name: Shine Slice
Shine Slice.description: charge and cut right thru your enemys. you are NOT immune to damage.

phaseout.name: Phase Shift
phaseout.description: Hold down the button to disappear from the world for up to 0.75 seconds. While phased shifted, you cannot be hurt, but you also cannot cast spells. Phase shift also cancels all knockback. Phase shift takes longer to cooldown the longer you stay in phase shift.

Light Ray.name: Light Ray
Light Ray.description: Shoot a ray at light speed damaging but travels thru enemys.

Fire Mines.name: Fire Mines
Fire Mines.description: Mark out your territory with some Fire Mines. If you walk away from the mines, they expire. Fire mines will also burn projectiles.

Frostbite.description: Fire a ray of ice that slows down an enemy by 20%.
Frostbite.name: frostbite

K Mines.name: Freezing Mines
K Mines.description: Mark your terriotry with Freezing Mines. These mines freeze upon impact.

Director.name: Lightwave
Director.description: Fire a ray that can be moved by your cursor.

Seekers.name: Backshot
Seekers.description: Fire 3 bolts behind your back and gain a boost.

OutBreak.name: OutBreak
OutBreak.description: Summon 16 bolts of toxic energy from the center of your player.

Cleanse.name: Cleanse
Cleanse.description: A quick Cleanse from knockback, positve and negitive effects.

Void Run.name: Void Run
Void Run.description: Travel to an alternite dimension for 2 secounds and pop back out anywhere.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

C Mines.name: Entrapment
C Mines.description: Form a circle around you to trap your enemys in. Last for 3.5 seconds.

Icicles.name: Icicles
Icicles.description: Fire 3 icicles that will slide back your enemy.

Radiation.name: GammaBall
Radiation.description: A toxic ball that will drain enemeys HP when their in the radius zone.

Ricocheter.name: Ricocheter
Ricocheter.description: Toss bouncer daggers that reflect off of objects and projectiles.
